step.datasource: SELECT TOP (1) 0 as DoQuit FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.isFolder = 0
SELECT l.ID, l.fullname, l.name FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0
SELECT l.ID, l.fullname, l.name FROM [%abeitargetdb%].dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0

UPDATE l WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus ,-1) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE -1 END , sysmessage = r.errormessage , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l LEFT JOIN [%abeidb%].dbo._AB_Entity_results r with (nolock) ON r.runid = l.runid and r.jobid = %jobid% and r.ExactProduct = 'File' and r.Action = 'read' and r.ReferenceValue = CAST(l.ID as varchar(100)) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0

UPDATE w WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = l.rowstatus , sysmessage = l.sysmessage , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment w INNER JOIN dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) ON l.runid = w.runid AND l.ID = w.FileFolderListID WHERE 1=1 AND w.runid = '%runid%' AND w.rowstatus = 0

UPDATE t WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET abei_deliverydate = t.order_deliverydate , abei_unitamount = t.orderline_unitamount , abei_ordernr = CASE WHEN ISNULL(k.afgehandld, 1) = 1 THEN '' ELSE k.ordernr END , abei_artcode = r.artcode , abei_isserialitem = i.isserialnumberitem , abei_orsrgID = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.uitgifte, 1) = 1 THEN 0 ELSE r.ID END
, rowstatus = CASE WHEN (k.ordernr IS NULL OR ISNULL(k.afgehandld, 1) = 1) OR (r.artcode IS NULL OR ISNULL(r.uitgifte, 1) = 1) OR (i.isserialnumberitem = 1 and isnull(t.orderline_lot,'') = '') OR (i.isserialnumberitem = 1 and abs(isnull(t.orderline_unitamount,0) - 1) > 0.1) THEN -1 ELSE 1 END , sysmessage = CASE WHEN k.ordernr IS NULL OR ISNULL(k.afgehandld, 1) = 1 THEN 'Order reference not valid' WHEN r.artcode IS NULL OR ISNULL(r.uitgifte, 1) = 1 THEN 'Article ID not valid' WHEN (i.isserialnumberitem = 1 and isnull(t.orderline_lot,'') = '') THEN 'No valid serial number' WHEN (i.isserialnumberitem = 1 and abs(isnull(t.orderline_unitamount,0) - 1) > 0.1) THEN 'Invalid amount for serial' ELSE t.sysmessage END , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
FROM [%abeitargetdb%].dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t inner join [%abeisourcedb%].dbo.items i with (NOLOCK) on t.orderline_article_id collate database_default = i.itemcode LEFT JOIN [%abeisourcedb%].dbo.orkrg k WITH (NOLOCK) ON k.ordernr = t.order_reference COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT OUTER APPLY ( -- select oldest orderline first SELECT TOP (1) r.ID, r.artcode, r.uitgifte FROM [%abeisourcedb%].dbo.orsrg r WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND r.ordernr = k.ordernr AND r.artcode = t.orderline_article_id COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT -- how do you want to join this? do you want to check on serialnumber? ORDER BY r.uitgifte, r.afldat ) r WHERE 1=1 AND t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1

SELECT t.abei_ordernr as HeaderID , t.abei_ordernr as Ordernr , t.abei_orsrgID as ID , t.abei_artcode as artcode , t.abei_deliverydate as afldat , t.abei_unitamount as esr_aantal FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1 and t.abei_isserialitem = 0

SELECT DISTINCT t.abei_ordernr as HeaderID , t.abei_ordernr as Ordernr , t.abei_deliverydate as ProcessDate , 1 as InvoiceGenerate , 0 as PrintMode -- Definitief (0 = Default) of Proef (1) , 2 as PrintDestination -- (0 = Default), Email (1) of Geen (2) FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1 and t.abei_isserialitem = 0

SELECT t.abei_ordernr as HeaderID , t.abei_ordernr as Ordernr , t.abei_orsrgID as ID , t.abei_artcode as artcode , t.abei_deliverydate as afldat --, t.abei_unitamount as esr_aantal , 1 as esr_aantal , t.orderline_lot as serie_num FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1 and t.abei_isserialitem = 1

SELECT DISTINCT t.abei_ordernr as HeaderID , t.abei_ordernr as Ordernr , t.abei_deliverydate as ProcessDate , 1 as InvoiceGenerate , 0 as PrintMode -- Definitief (0 = Default) of Proef (1) , 2 as PrintDestination -- (0 = Default), Email (1) of Geen (2) FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1 and t.abei_isserialitem = 1

UPDATE t WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus ,-1) = 2 THEN 2 ELSE -1 END , sysmessage = ISNULL(r.errormessage, 'No result found') , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t LEFT JOIN [%abeidb%].dbo._AB_Entity_results r with (nolock) ON r.runid = t.runid and r.jobid = %jobid% and ((t.isserialitem = 1 and r.jobstepid = 3855) or (t.isserialitem = 0 and r.jobstepid = 3436)) and r.HeaderID = t.abei_ordernr WHERE 1=1 AND t.runid = '%runid%' AND t.rowstatus = 1

SELECT DISTINCT b.document as Document, (b.filename) as New_filename
FROM [ABSC_Data].._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment t INNER JOIN [400]..BacoDiscussions b ON B.OrderNumber = t.order_reference COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT AND B.TYPE = 12 Where 1 = 1 AND t.runid = '%runid%'
step.contentbody:
We are pleased to inform you that the attached orders have been processed at Orlaco.

For your convenience, we have included the corresponding PDFs. Please ensure that the delivery notes are incorporated into the paperwork for the weekly shipment.

If you have any questions or concerns, please feel free to reach out to us at Order.Netherlands@Stoneridge.com.


Thank you,

Stoneridge | ORLACO – Vision is our mission®

step.datasource: UPDATE l WITH (ROWLOCK, NOWAIT) SET rowstatus = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus, -1) = 2 THEN 2 ELSE -1 END , sysmessage = CASE WHEN ISNULL(r.rowstatus,-1) = 2 THEN 'Success' ELSE 'Error, check WarehouseShipment table for details' END , sysmodified = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l OUTER APPLY ( SELECT MIN(w.rowstatus) as rowstatus FROM dbo._AB_tb_VanReenen_WarehouseShipment w WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND w.runid = l.runid AND w.FileFolderListID = l.ID ) r WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0 AND l.rowstatus = 1
SELECT l.ID, l.name FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0 AND l.rowstatus = 2
SELECT l.ID, l.name FROM dbo._AB_tb_ABEI_FileFolder_List l WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE 1=1 AND l.runid = '%runid%' AND l.jobid = %jobid% AND l.isFolder = 0 AND l.rowstatus <> 2
